                "SITA",
                "EDE",
                "COINC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " In the experiment, the alphas",
                "and deuterons from the breakup of 6Li were detected,",
                "while the elastically scattered 6Li ions were swept",
                "out by the magnetic field of the MAGNEX spectrometer.",
                "The background due to elastic scattering was further",
                "reduced by using offline cuts in the dE-E spectra.",
                "Experimental data were limited to forward angles",
                " (first kinematic solution) due to the detector",
                "configuration. Detection efficiency was estimated by",
                "Monte Carlo simulation."
              ]
            }
          ],
